snippet.title: Exterior or External Angles of a Polygon and Sum of exterior angles (Derivation)
snippet.description:
Learn what are exterior angles of a polygon. Also learn to find sum of exterior angles of a polygon. Derivation of formula using algebra.

For more such videos visit or subscribe to my YouTube channel https://www.youtube.com/MathsSmart
